---
title     : Assay
summary   : Class-based Assertions Framework
license   : Apache 2.0
suite     : rubyworks
created   : 2009-08-21

authors:
  - Thomas Sawyer

description:
  The Assay project defines Assertions in the same way that Ruby
  defines Exceptions. An asserition then simply becomes an extension
  to an Exception class.

